P\left(W_{m+1}|W_{m}\right)=P\left(W_{m+1}\cap W_{m}\right)/P\left(W_{m}\right)=P\left(W_{m+1}\right)/P\left(W_{m}\right)=\frac{1}{m+2}/\frac{1}{m+1}=\frac{m+1}{m+2}
